<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="57" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="57">
This species is included in 
<taxonomicName authority="P.M.Peterson, K.Romaschenko, R.J.Soreng &amp; S.P.Sylvester, 2020" authorityName="P. M. Peterson, Romasch., Soreng &amp; Sylvester" authorityYear="2020" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Alpagrostis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Alpagrostis" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Alpagrostis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on its similar morphology, although this needs to be confirmed in molecular analyses. Certain characteristics sometimes differ from the other species in the genus, i.e., spikelets and lemmas sometimes shorter, insertion of the awn sometimes higher on the lemma, panicle branches and pedicels smooth or scaberulous. 
<taxonomicName authority="P.M.Peterson, K.Romaschenko, R.J.Soreng &amp; S.P.Sylvester, 2020" authorityName="P. M. Peterson, Romasch., Soreng &amp; Sylvester" authorityYear="2020" baseAuthorityName="P. M. Peterson, Romasch., Soreng &amp; Sylvester" baseAuthorityYear="2020" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Alpagrostis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Alpagrostis barceloi" order="Poales" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="barceloi">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">Alpagrostis barceloi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
shares with other member of the genus, conduplicate leaf blades, truncate lemma apices with setaceous extensions of the lateral veins, and ecologically is a strict orophyte, much like 
<taxonomicName genus="A." lsidName="A. alpina" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" rank="species" species="alpina">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">A. alpina</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName genus="A." lsidName="A. schleicheri" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" rank="species" species="schleicheri">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="57">A. schleicheri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1095-8339.2000.tb01551.x" author="Saez, L" journalOrPublisher="Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society" pageId="0" pageNumber="57" pagination="359 - 370" refId="B35" refString="Saez, L, Rossello, JA, 2000. A new species of Agrostis (Gramineae) in the A. alpina complex. Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society 133 (3): 359 - 370, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1095-8339.2000.tb01551.x" title="A new species of Agrostis (Gramineae) in the A. alpina complex." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1095-8339.2000.tb01551.x" volume="133" year="2000">
<normalizedToken originalValue="Sáez">Saez</normalizedToken>
and 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Rosselló">Rossello</normalizedToken>
2000
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
